"}, {"viewer_has_update_access": false, "full_applications": {"nodes": [{"id": "2051702344842370"}]}, "id": "286019738802476"}, {"viewer_has_update_access": false, "full_applications": {"nodes": [{"id": "1692021557498395"}]}, "id": "166555960611255"}, {"viewer_has_update_access": false, "full_applications": {"nodes": [{"id": "967457083325115"}]}, "id": "235253180196091"}, {"viewer_has_update_access": false, "full_applications": {"nodes": [{"id": "743301119132072"}]}, "id": "1730741243876997"}]}}, "firstRevision": {"nodes": [{"application": {"id": "3634830803298285", "release_date": 1620320417, "is_concept": false, "platform": "ANDROID_6DOF", "scheduled_offers": {"count": 43}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "7550445625070097"}, "id": "1034944893649319"}]}}, "binary": null, "live_binary": null, "created_date": 1701800084, "id": "6849472995167367", "is_initial_release": false, "name_with_fallback": "v29", "pdp_metadata_with_fallback": {"version": 28, "application": {"is_concept": false, "latest_released_pdp_metadata": {"id": "6849472991834034"}, "release_status": "RELEASED", "id": "3634830803298285"}, "id": "6849472991834034", "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED"}, "release_date": null, "administration_status": "APPROVED", "is_first": false, "release_status": "RELEASED", "release_type": "SCHEDULED", "pdp_metadata": {"application": {"default_locale": "en_US", "id": "3634830803298285", "is_first_party": false, "enables_in_app_ads": false, "is_concept": false, "platform": "ANDROID_6DOF"}, "iarc_cert": {"id": "317291880052134"}, "iarc_email": null, "msrp": null, "translations": {"nodes": [{"images": {"nodes": []}, "id": "3188732411433952", "locale": "de_DE", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Demeo", "keywords": ["Mehrspieler", "Social", "RPG", "Dungeon", "Tabletop"], "long_description": "Abenteurer, vereinigt euch! Versammelt eure Freunde und bek\u00e4mpft Monster in Demeo, dem rundenbasierten Tabletop-Strategiespiel.\n \nW\u00fcrfelt, nehmt eure Miniaturen und befreit die Welt von Gilmerra in diesem spannenden Tabletop-Brettspiel! Bei der gro\u00dfen Auswahl an Monstern, Klassen und Umgebungen, die es zu erkunden gilt, ist jedes Spiel anders!\n  \nF\u00dcNF KOMPLETTE ABENTEUER\n\u25cf Der schwarze Sarkophag \n\u25cf Reich des Rattenk\u00f6nigs\n\u25cf Wurzeln des B\u00f6sen \n\u25cf Fluch des Schlangenherrn\n\u25cf Herrschaft des Wahnsinns\n \nHELDENTREFF\n\u25cf Neue Freunde treffen\n\u25cf Miniaturen bemalen\n\u25cf Bogenschie\u00dfwettk\u00e4mpfe\n\u25cf Arkadenspiel \u201eThe Hauntlet\u201c\n\u25cf Hol dir Tipps, Tricks und Hintergr\u00fcnde\n\nPassthrough-Modus f\u00fcr Quest 2 + Vollfarb-Passthrough f\u00fcr Quest Pro\n\nDemeo \u2013 Ein Tabletop-Fantasy-Spiel von den Elfen-Handwerkern bei Resolution Games", "short_description": "Abenteurer, es ist Zeit, sich zu vereinen! Im RPG-Dungeoncrawler Demeo hat eine dunkle Macht die Unterwelt \u00fcbernommen, und allein kann das keiner \u00fcberleben. Versammelt bis zu vier Spieler, um die unheilige Macht zu bezwingen, die die 5. Welt korrumpiert ... oder sterbt bei dem Versuch."}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "KOSquare.png", "id": "914705989982417", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_SQUARE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982613_914705993315750_389193327039745621_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=o3h7POEuC1gQ7kNvgFjpPb2&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYA-CV5V5drRKhJw_UPBgM7VgpgYwIDjxrB4bU_6mnaJSg&oe=670E58CD"}, {"file_name": "KOHero-Cover.png", "id": "733359001752903", "image_type": "APP_IMG_HERO", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035463_733359005086236_5213611436012827733_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=JLLGTZJAP_QQ7kNvgHSTfYC&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB9wB6vAzZc_4SNoGIQ4TpoCqSn0jG1J7AzAkdYqNmvmw&oe=670E5395"}, {"file_name": "icon_512x512 (1).png", "id": "687829673031833", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57569472_687829676365166_8041040940019835697_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=6VfaRyiDKQgQ7kNvgHTuD-0&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBgK-hlRjWmq8AWkRCfrhFigGACaieGDFXdsFbWt5dcIg&oe=670E3B29"}, {"file_name": "KOMini-Landscape.png", "id": "595948079095882", "image_type": "APP_IMG_SMALL_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974450_595948082429215_5331379934404377219_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=iEngFvX-XaUQ7kNvgH7FavK&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCwCXkOJ4VpS3AArzB8gYCQwHy_41J4_aiS5eVXHYkYIQ&oe=670E6CEA"}, {"file_name": "KOLandscape.png", "id": "202170052458397", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75223485_202170055791730_282571275818168555_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=jqDcpet_eGMQ7kNvgFlHQIX&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCqS8lqQLTHhnT649mER83FV1cfvSYL9QT0gOUmg9-t9w&oe=670E7122"}, {"file_name": "logo_2560x1440_KO (3).png", "id": "183000364481232", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035469_183000367814565_2047698377128427738_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=YIKxAiDU4QgQ7kNvgF5f4c-&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYD8-4EsM0PocsnBArmdnrtx6up6J-xKr8ok7ZNw0QTnMA&oe=670E5C6E"}, {"file_name": "KOPortrait.png", "id": "142096358787655", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974525_142096362120988_8577255514254648318_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=rUU0AUK7WSgQ7kNvgEij0q7&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAAW_U4JogHQT1LEahmwAxuz5vChIbSDRJ0gs_cyWLhjg&oe=670E6838"}]}, "id": "870085461441264", "locale": "ko_KR", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "\ub370\uba54\uc624: \ub358\uc804 \ud06c\ub864\ub7ec VR", "keywords": ["\uba40\ud2f0\ud50c\ub808\uc774", "\uc18c\uc15c", "RPG", "\ub358\uc804", "\ud14c\uc774\ube14\ud0d1"], "long_description": "\ubaa8\ud5d8\uac00 \uc5ec\ub7ec\ubd84, \uc5b4\uc11c \uc9d1\uacb0\ud558\uc138\uc694! \uc804\ub7b5 \ud134\uc81c TRPG \ub370\uba54\uc624\uc5d0\uc11c \uce5c\uad6c\ub4e4\uc744 \ubaa8\uc544 \uc0ac\uc545\ud55c \uc874\uc7ac\uc5d0 \ub9de\uc11c \uc2f8\uc6b0\uace0 \uc601\uad11\uc744 \ucc28\uc9c0\ud558\uc138\uc694.\n \n\ub9d0\uc744 \uc190\uc5d0 \uafb9 \uc950\uace0 \uc8fc\uc0ac\uc704\ub97c \uad74\ub9ac\uba70, \uae38\uba54\ub77c\ub97c \uc790\uc720\ub86d\uac8c \ud65c\ubcf4\ud558\uc138\uc694. \uadf8\ub9ac\uace0 TRPG \ud2b9\uc720\uc758 \uc7ac\ubbf8\ub97c \ud55c\uaecf \ub204\ub824\ubcf4\uc138\uc694. \ubc29\ub300\ud55c \uc885\ub958\uc758 \uad34\ubb3c, \ud50c\ub808\uc774 \uac00\ub2a5 \ud074\ub798\uc2a4 \ubc0f \uac8c\uc784 \uc9c4\ud589\uc5d0 \ub530\ub77c \uc0dd\uc131\ub418\ub294 \ud0d0\ud5d8 \ud658\uacbd \ub4f1, \uc9c0\uae08\uae4c\uc9c0 \ubcfc \uc218 \uc5c6\uc5c8\ub358 \ub3c5\ud2b9\ud568\uc73c\ub85c \ubb34\uc7a5\ud55c \uac8c\uc784\uc785\ub2c8\ub2e4.\n  \n\ub2e4\uc12f \uac1c\uc758 \uc644\uacb0\ub41c \ubaa8\ud5d8\n\u25cf \uac80\uc740 \uc11d\uad00 \n\u25cf \uc655\uc950\uac00 \ub2e4\uc2a4\ub9ac\ub294 \uacf3\n\u25cf \uc0ac\uc545\ud55c \ubfcc\ub9ac \n\u25cf \ud070\ubc40\uc2e0\uc758 \uc800\uc8fc\n\u25cf \uad70\ub9bc\ud558\ub294 \uad11\uae30\n \n\uc601\uc6c5\uc758 \ud734\uac8c\uc18c\n\u25cf \uc0c8 \uce5c\uad6c \uc0ac\uadc0\uae30\n\u25cf \ub9d0\uc5d0 \uc0c9\uce60\ud558\uae30\n\u25cf \uad81\uc220 \uc5f0\ub9c8\ud558\uae30\n\u25cf '\ub370\uba54\uc624 \ub354 \ud5cc\ud2c0\ub81b' \ud50c\ub808\uc774\n\u25cf \ud301, \ud2b8\ub9ad \ubc0f \uc774\uc57c\uae30 \uc0b4\ud3b4\ubcf4\uae30\n\nQuest 2\uc6a9 \ud328\uc2a4\uc2a4\ub8e8 \ubaa8\ub4dc \ubc0f Quest Pro\uc6a9 \ud480\uceec\ub7ec \ud328\uc2a4\uc2a4\ub8e8 \ubaa8\ub4dc\n\nResolution Games\uc758 \uc694\uc815\uc871 \uae30\uc220\uc790\ub4e4\uc774 \uc120\uc0ac\ud558\ub294 \ud658\uc0c1\uc758 TRPG \ub370\uba54\uc624", "short_description": "\ubaa8\ud5d8\uac00 \uc5ec\ub7ec\ubd84, \uc5b4\uc11c \uc9d1\uacb0\ud558\uc138\uc694! \ub358\uc804 \ud0d0\uc0c9 RPG \ub370\uba54\uc624\uc758 \uc9c0\ud558\uc138\uacc4\ub97c \uc5b4\ub460\uc758 \uc138\ub825\uc774 \uc815\ubcf5\ud588\uc2b5\ub2c8\ub2e4. \uc774\uacf3\uc740 \ud63c\uc790\uc11c\ub294 \ubaa9\uc228\uc744 \ubd80\uc9c0\ud560 \uc218 \uc5c6\uc73c\ub2c8 \ucd5c\ub300 4\uba85\uc758 \ud50c\ub808\uc774\uc5b4\uac00 \ud798\uc744 \ubaa8\uc544 \uc81c5 \uc138\uacc4\ub97c \ub354\ub7fd\ud788\ub294 \ubd80\uc815\ud55c \uc874\uc7ac\ub97c \ud568\uaed8 \ud574\uce58\uc6cc\uc57c \ud569\ub2c8\ub2e4. \ubb3c\ub860... \uadf8 \uc2dc\ub3c4\uac00 \ub298 \uc131\uacf5\ud558\uc9c0\ub294 \uc54a\uaca0\uc9c0\ub9cc\uc694."}, {"images": {"nodes": []}, "id": "869626557994057", "locale": "es_LA", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Demeo", "keywords": ["multijugador", "social", "rpg", "calabozo", "mesa"], "long_description": "Aventureros, es hora de unirse. Re\u00fane a tus amigos y lucha contra los monstruos en Demeo, un juego de estrategia de mesa por turnos lleno de batallas y gloria.\n \nTira los dados, mueve miniaturas y libera el mundo de Gilmerra sobre la mesa. La partida nunca se repite gracias a una selecci\u00f3n enorme de monstruos, clases jugables y entornos para explorar.\n  \nCINCO AVENTURAS COMPLETAS\n\u25cf El sarc\u00f3fago negro \n\u25cf Reino del rey rata\n\u25cf Ra\u00edces del mal \n\u25cf Maldici\u00f3n del dios serpentino\n\u25cf Reinado de locura\n \nREUNI\u00d3N DE PERSONAJES\n\u25cf Conoce amigos nuevos\n\u25cf Pinta miniaturas\n\u25cf Compite en arquer\u00eda\n\u25cf Disfruta del juego de acci\u00f3n Hauntlet\n\u25cf Recibe consejos, trucos y conocimiento\n\nModo passthrough en Quest 2 + y passthrough a todo color en Quest Pro\n\nDemeo: un juego de mesa de fantas\u00eda creado por los art\u00edfices de Resolution Games", "short_description": "Lleg\u00f3 el momento de unirse, aventureros. Una fuerza oscura conquista el inframundo en Demeo, un juego de rol y exploraci\u00f3n de calabozos en el que no sobrevivir\u00e1s sin ayuda. Colabora con hasta otros cuatro jugadores para desterrar la fuerza imp\u00eda que corrompe al 5\u00ba mundo o morir en el intento."}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "JA_Mini-Landscape.png", "id": "8915591531848609", "image_type": "APP_IMG_SMALL_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39003260_8915591541848608_8138226255033756710_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=m9MYxNl1e3UQ7kNvgHCSng0&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDzp4jAE0CvFuYGRqjHM_kiOzaH4MsQdyb4v3pkr1JPNQ&oe=670E4084"}, {"file_name": "icon_512x512 (1).png", "id": "3460567307550632", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39036608_3460567310883965_442104228139607100_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=EdFrFBbzek8Q7kNvgGs_bHh&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYD3hqtwomSrh_16p6yLS4LVGjOzrXTHnuCkkIJ1ztAlmQ&oe=670E4CA9"}, {"file_name": "JA_Square.png", "id": "730088528612863", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_SQUARE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982469_730088531946196_6909616479504378337_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Lsy-qX4r4DQQ7kNvgFZCpfj&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDQSsaALbvpG7tPXRJnyi6OSNnnyDDOnRXZa9nrppC0-Q&oe=670E469D"}, {"file_name": "JA_Landscape.png", "id": "609102880647893", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974905_609102883981226_3277093904103825954_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=ouIKaPSFAUIQ7kNvgEfaqEo&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCrpBFLCWRMHiadMzj71JQFZrfjzwEb