092\u56f2\u3093\u3067\u30b5\u30a4\u30b3\u30ed\u3092\u632f\u308d\u3046\uff01VR\u30c0\u30f3\u30b8\u30e7\u30f3\u653b\u7565RPG\u300e\u30c7\u30e1\u30aa: \u30c0\u30f3\u30b8\u30e7\u30f3 \u30a2\u30c9\u30d9\u30f3\u30c1\u30e3\u30fc\u300f\u306f\u3001\u53cb\u9054\u306e\u8ab0\u304b\u306e\u5bb6\u3084\u5730\u5143\u306e\u516c\u6c11\u9928\u3067\u96c6\u307e\u308b\u4ee3\u308f\u308a\u306b\u3001VR\u7a7a\u9593\u3067\u30c6\u30fc\u30d6\u30eb\u3092\u56f2\u3093\u3067\u30b5\u30a4\u30b3\u30ed\u3092\u632f\u308c\u308b\u30b2\u30fc\u30e0\u3060\u3002\u6700\u59274\u4eba\u306e\u30d7\u30ec\u30a4\u30e4\u30fc\u3067\u30d1\u30fc\u30c6\u30a3\u30fc\u3092\u7d44\u307f\u3001\u6050\u6016\u3068\u8ca1\u5b9d\u306b\u7acb\u3061\u5411\u304b\u304a\u3046\u3002\u300c\u7b2c\u4e94\u4e16\u754c\u300d\u3092\u8150\u6557\u3055\u305b\u3093\u3068\u3059\u308b\u4e0d\u6d44\u306a\u308b\u8ecd\u56e3\u3092\u6253\u3061\u7834\u308c\u308b\u306e\u304b\u2026\u305d\u308c\u3068\u3082\u9014\u4e2d\u3067\u529b\u5c3d\u304d\u308b\u306e\u304b\u3002"}, {"images": {"nodes": []}, "id": "844889730765142", "locale": "fr_FR", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Demeo", "keywords": ["Multijoueur", "Social", "RPG", "Donjon", "Plateau"], "long_description": "Aventuriers, unissez-vous ! Rassemblez vos amis et affrontez des monstres dans Demeo, le jeu de strat\u00e9gie sur table au tour par tour.\n \nLancez vos d\u00e9s, choisissez vos figurines et lib\u00e9rez le monde de Gilmerra ! Avec un large \u00e9ventail de monstres, de classes jouables et d'environnements g\u00e9n\u00e9r\u00e9s de mani\u00e8re proc\u00e9durale, chaque partie est diff\u00e9rente.\n  \nCINQ AVENTURES INT\u00c9GRALES\n\u25cf Sarcophage noir \n\u25cf Royaume du roi des rats\n\u25cf Racines du mal \n\u25cf Mal\u00e9diction du seigneur serpent\n\u25cf R\u00e8gne de la folie\n \nREPAIRE DES H\u00c9ROS\n\u25cf Faites-vous de nouveaux amis\n\u25cf Peignez des figurines\n\u25cf Affrontez-vous au tir \u00e0 l'arc\n\u25cf Jouez au jeu d'arcade r\u00e9tro\n\u25cf D\u00e9couvrez des conseils, astuces et histoires\n\nMode Passthrough sur Quest 2 + passthrough tout en couleur sur Quest Pro\n\nDemeo, le jeu de plateau fantastique des artificiers elfes de Resolution Games", "short_description": "Aventuriers, l\u2019heure est venue de vous unir ! Une force sombre s\u2019est empar\u00e9e de l\u2019outremonde du dungeon crawler RPG, Demeo, et vous avez peu de chances d\u2019y survivre sans aide. R\u00e9unissez jusqu\u2019\u00e0 quatre joueurs et collaborez pour vaincre les forces impies qui corrompent le 5e monde... ou mourez en essayant."}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "CHS_Landscape.png", "id": "3395339474014708", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57568670_3395339477348041_5739749501286752069_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=FOcBQrkBXAoQ7kNvgHZfruo&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDbiW4LExjlQZKwV3CbJ3p8c0emajBazVEd9PwRdPGqoQ&oe=670E5E66"}, {"file_name": "CHS_Hero-Cover.png", "id": "3037236439918849", "image_type": "APP_IMG_HERO", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974732_3037236443252182_4563562955561084884_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=lUvv3mDXLwMQ7kNvgF3iG5n&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCcaAruc-usUpGVuUWMhayqBXiHWx1xy1dkfY5Xl6rblA&oe=670E57DF"}, {"file_name": "CHS_Square.png", "id": "3001535033486122", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_SQUARE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031434_3001535036819455_42426308471192022_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=sOtXdFL0gTwQ7kNvgHrU5Kq&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYD-XO9ghQKnpeM_qbpj4TJofoF4lGaKjFc91PwUVdiqgQ&oe=670E3D4F"}, {"file_name": "CHS_Portrait.png", "id": "647551713802929", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974636_647551717136262_6137763898081506559_n.p