iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB_BWNSZW63s4DVTJIcajfa-1ETcVtgPrKtAw54nIkVjg&oe=670E44FF"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "EN_Landscape.png", "id": "203808565627458", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974924_203808568960791_2901843682204848968_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=geSMNNFhlhoQ7kNvgFdC70P&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAuLmiqDQox9sl3Nyj5_FAmfU-CQFb8XexWZIFvabckew&oe=670E68CD"}, "display_name": "Demeo", "keywords": ["multiplayer", "social", "rpg", "dungeon", "tabletop"], "long_description": "Adventurers, it\u2019s time to unite! Gather your friends and fight monsters in Demeo, the turn-based tabletop strategy game of battle and glory.\n \nRoll dice, pick up miniatures, and free the world of Gilmerra in round after round of tabletop board game fun. With a huge assortment of monsters, playable classes, and environments to explore, it\u2019s never the same game twice.\n  \nFIVE COMPLETE ADVENTURES\n\u25cf The Black Sarcophagus \n\u25cf Realm of the Rat King\n\u25cf Roots of Evil \n\u25cf Curse of the Serpent Lord\n\u25cf Reign of Madness\n \nHEROES\u2019 HANGOUT\n\u25cf Meet new friends\n\u25cf Paint miniatures\n\u25cf Compete in archery\n\u25cf Play the \u2018Hauntlet\u2019 arcade game\n\u25cf Learn tips, tricks, and lore\n\nMixed reality mode available on Quest 2 + full-color passthrough on Quest Pro\n\nDemeo \u2014 a game of tabletop fantasy from the Elven artificers at Resolution Games", "short_description": "Adventurers, it\u2019s time to unite! Gather your friends and battle the dark forces that have overtaken the world of Resolution Games' award-winning RPG dungeon crawler, Demeo. The next generation of tabletop adventure has arrived!"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.resolutiongames.com/privacy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://www.resolutiongames.com/terms-of-use", "publisher_name": "Resolution Games", 